</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_498" id="248v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_498_r1l1"><expan>Altman<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_498_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan></del> <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hofmeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> / Es iſt etwas red an vns kumen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l3">das ettlich <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> Juden <expan>antreffe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſolt als wir mainen / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l4">Jr das nu auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd dauon gehort habt / Nu <expan>vviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l5">wir der ſache nicht gruntlich / vnd <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> vvir ewr <expan>Erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l6">cʒemal <expan>fleıſſıgl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / was ew <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>handlu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l7">wegen wiſſentlich ſeẏ / daʒ Jr vns das / als vil ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l8">fuglich ſeẏ an <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>m</expan> brief <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wollet / beẏ diſem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l9">boten / daʒ vvir vns in den dingen darnach <expan>deſt<ex>er</ex>bas</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_498_r1l10">gerichten mügen / das wollen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_498" id="248v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Altman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, es ist etwas red an uns kumen, das
                        ettlich <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan> juden
                            <expan>antreffe<ex>n</ex></expan> solt, als wir mainen, daz ir das nu
                        auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und davon gehort habt. Nu
                                <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir der sache nicht gruntlich und
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        czemal <expan>fleissigl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, was ew
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>handlu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und sache wegen wissentlich sey, daz ir uns
                        das, als vil ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> fuglich sey, an
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>m</expan> brief
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wollet bey disem
                        boten, daz wir uns in den dingen darnach <expan>dest<ex>er</ex>bas</expan>
                        gerichten mügen. Das wollen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
